title: El Arbol
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Juice bar, Catering, Chilean, Latin American
description: Vegetarian and mostly organic cafe and shop. The shop and kitchen is on the first floor, and the cafe is on the second floor. Inexpensive set meal with bread, soup, dish, juice, and dessert are available 12:30-3pm. The menu itself offers sandwiches, salads, and simple main dishes. Relaxed atmosphere, decoration of wood and mud-like walls. Has Wi-Fi.
